\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/6-300x300.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/6-300x300.png\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Hi\\u1ec7n nay,&nbsp;xo\\u00e0i H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c&nbsp;\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ed3ng r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i \\u1edf nh\\u1eefng v\\u00f9ng thu\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1eb1ng S\\u00f4ng C\\u1eedu Long. Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, t\\u1ec9nh \\u0110\\u1ed3ng Th\\u00e1p l\\u00e0 ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn nh\\u1ea5t, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t khi th\\u1ee9c qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00f2n g\\u1eafn li\\u1ec1n v\\u1edbi t\\u00ean g\\u1ecdi kh\\u00e1c \\u201cxo\\u00e0i Cao L\\u00e3nh\\u201d. Th\\u1ebf nh\\u01b0ng, theo nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u00ecnh ch\\u1ecdn t\\u1eeb d\\u00e2n s\\u00e0nh \\u0103n, lo\\u1ea1i xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t ngon nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1eabn l\\u00e0 xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9 t\\u1eeb C\\u00e1i B\\u00e8 \\u2013 Ti\\u1ec1n Giang.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><i><strong>Xem th\\u00eam:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/i><a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/meo-phan-biet-cac-loai-xoai-cat-chu-va-xoai-hoa-loc.html\\\"><i><strong><u>M\\u1eb9o ph\\u00e2n bi\\u1ec7t c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t chu v\\u00e0 xo\\u00e0i H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c<\\/u><\\/strong><\\/i><\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><i><strong>Xem th\\u00eam:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/i><a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/xoai-cat-hoa-loc.html\\\"><i><strong><u>C\\u00e1ch nh\\u1eadn bi\\u1ebft xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c<\\/u><\\/strong><\\/i><\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Gi\\u1ed1ng&nbsp;<strong>xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9<\\/strong>c c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 cho \\u0111\\u01a1m hoa sau 2 n\\u0103m, v\\u1edbi th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u01a1m hoa \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi thu ho\\u1ea1ch l\\u00e0 kho\\u1ea3ng 4 th\\u00e1ng. Sau khi c\\u00e2y \\u0111\\u1eadu tr\\u00e1i, t\\u1eebng qu\\u1ea3 xo\\u00e0i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u00e0 n\\u00f4ng bao tr\\u00e1i r\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea9n th\\u1eadn. Vi\\u1ec7c n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n nh\\u1eb1m b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 tr\\u00e1i kh\\u1ecfi c\\u00f4n tr\\u00f9ng g\\u00e2y h\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0 d\\u1ecbch b\\u1ec7nh. H\\u01a1n n\\u1eefa, ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p c\\u00f2n gi\\u00fap qu\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 an to\\u00e0n h\\u01a1n cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>2. M\\u00f9a v\\u1ee5 &amp; thu ho\\u1ea1ch xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c \\u1edf Vi\\u1ec7t Nam<\\/strong><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Theo \\u0111\\u00f3,&nbsp;<strong>m\\u00f9a v\\u1ee5 xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9<\\/strong>c ch\\u00ednh v\\u1ee5 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng di\\u1ec5n ra v\\u00e0o th\\u00e1ng 4 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 5. M\\u1eb7t kh\\u00e1c, m\\u00f9a c\\u1ee7a gi\\u1ed1ng n\\u00e0y n\\u00e0y mu\\u1ed9n h\\u01a1n s\\u1ebd t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 7 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 9. V\\u1edbi th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m tr\\u00e1i m\\u00f9a l\\u00e0 v\\u00e0o th\\u00e1ng 12 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 1 n\\u0103m sau.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c c\\u00f3 ngu\\u1ed3n g\\u1ed1c ngon nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 t\\u1ea1i x\\u00e3 H\\u00f2a H\\u01b0ng, huy\\u1ec7n C\\u00e1i B\\u00e8, t\\u1ec9nh Ti\\u1ec1n Giang. V\\u00ec v\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 th\\u1ed5 nh\\u1eefng thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i, t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n t\\u1ed1t cho c\\u00e2y xo\\u00e0i ra qu\\u1ea3 v\\u00e0 ngon h\\u01a1n c\\u00e1c n\\u01a1i kh\\u00e1c.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng,&nbsp;<strong>m\\u00f9a v\\u1ee5 xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c<\\/strong>&nbsp;ngon nh\\u1ea5t th\\u01b0\\u1eddng di\\u1ec5n ra v\\u00e0o m\\u00f9a thu\\u1eadn m\\u1ed7i n\\u0103m. C\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 4 \\u0111\\u1ebfn h\\u1ebft th\\u00e1ng 5 m\\u1ed7i n\\u0103m. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 ngon h\\u01a1n h\\u1eb3n m\\u00f9a mu\\u1ed9n v\\u00e0 m\\u00f9a ngh\\u1ecbch. V\\u00e0o m\\u00f9a thu\\u1eadn, qu\\u1ea3 xo\\u00e0i c\\u00f3 ph\\u1ea7n hai m\\u00e1 c\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ea7y, tr\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u1ec1u, to kh\\u1ecfe v\\u00e0 ch\\u1eafc tay. Qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00f3 h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u01a1m n\\u1ed3ng n\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 quy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169 kh\\u00f3 c\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);col