g class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-72670 entered litespeed-loaded\\\" style=\\\"border-style:none;height:auto;max-width:100%;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/3-300x300.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/3-300x300.png\\\"><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>5. L\\u01b0u \\u00fd b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n v\\u00e0 cam k\\u1ebft ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u1ee7a xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c t\\u1ea1i VinFruits<\\/strong><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">C\\u00e1ch b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c b\\u1eb1ng ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p \\u0111\\u00f3ng h\\u1ed9p:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;list-style:none;margin:0px 0px 1.5em;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:5px;\\\"><strong>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 1:<\\/strong>&nbsp;G\\u1ecdt th\\u1eadt s\\u1ea1ch v\\u1ecf xo\\u00e0i, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u1eaft th\\u00e0nh t\\u1eebng mi\\u1ebfng xo\\u00e0i l\\u1edbn ra kh\\u1ecfi h\\u1ea1t. Ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c, \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u00e1c mi\\u1ebfng xo\\u00e0i l\\u1edbn l\\u00ean th\\u1edbt v\\u00e0 c\\u1eaft th\\u00e0nh c\\u00e1c mi\\u1ebfng nh\\u1ecf kho\\u1ea3ng 2,5cm.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:5px;\\\"><strong>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 2:<\\/strong>&nbsp;Cho c\\u00e1c mi\\u1ebfng xo\\u00e0i nh\\u1ecf v\\u00e0o m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ecd kh\\u00f4 r\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 s\\u1ea1ch. Kh\\u00f4ng n\\u00ean cho v\\u00e