rong>Sau khi c\\u00e1c l\\u1ecd \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1eed l\\u00fd, h\\u00e3y \\u0111\\u1ec3 ngu\\u1ed9i t\\u1eeb 2-3 ti\\u1ebfng. Trong th\\u1eddi gian n\\u00e0y, n\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ecd \\u1edf n\\u01a1i tr\\u00e1nh \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 d\\u01b0\\u1edbi 24 \\u00b0C. V\\u1edbi<strong>&nbsp;c\\u00e1ch b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n xo\\u00e0i<\\/strong>&nbsp;c\\u00e1t H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00f3ng h\\u1ed9p s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 th\\u1eddi h\\u1ea1n t\\u1eeb 1-2 n\\u0103m.<\\/li><\\/ul><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-72672 entered litespeed-loaded\\\" style=\\\"border-style:none;height:auto;max-width:100%;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/5-300x300.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/5-300x300.png\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">B\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n b\\u1eb1ng ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p s\\u1ea5y kh\\u00f4:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;list-style:none;margin:0px 0px 1.5em;padding:0px 0px 0px 16px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><li style=\\\"margin-bottom:5px;\\\"><strong>B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 1:<\\/strong>&nbsp;L\\u00e0m n\\u00f3ng l\\u00f2 \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 th\\u1ea5p nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3. H\\u1ea7u h\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c l\\u00f2 n\\u01b0\\u1edbng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 xu\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5p t\\u1edbi 93 