ope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-72667 entered litespeed-loaded\\\" style=\\\"border-style:none;height:auto;max-width:100%;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/6-300x300.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/6-300x300.png\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Hi\\u1ec7n nay,&nbsp;xo\\u00e0i H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c&nbsp;\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ed3ng r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i \\u1edf nh\\u1eefng v\\u00f9ng thu\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u1eb1ng S\\u00f4ng C\\u1eedu Long. Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, t\\u1ec9nh \\u0110\\u1ed3ng Th\\u00e1p l\\u00e0 ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn nh\\u1ea5t, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t khi th\\u1ee9c qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00f2n g\\u1eafn li\\u1ec1n v\\u1edbi t\\u00ean g\\u1ecdi kh\\u00e1c \\u201cxo\\u00e0i Cao L\\u00e3nh\\u201d. Th\\u1ebf nh\\u01b0ng, theo nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u00ecnh ch\\u1ecdn t\\u1eeb d\\u00e2n s\\u00e0nh \\u0103n, lo\\u1ea1i xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t ngon nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1eabn l\\u00e0 xu\\u1ea5t x\\u1ee9 t\\u1eeb C\\u00e1i B\\u00e8 \\u2013 Ti\\u1ec1n Giang.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><i><strong>Xem th\\u00eam:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/i><a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/meo-phan-biet-cac-loai-xoai-cat-chu-va-xoai-hoa-loc.html\\\"><i><strong><u>M\\u1eb9o ph\\u00e2n bi\\u1ec7t c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i xo\\u00e0i c\\u00e1t chu v\\u00e0 xo\\u00e0i H\\u00f2a L\\u1ed9c<\\/u><\\/strong><\\/i><\\/a><\\/p><p styl