00f2n, v\\u1ecf m\\u00e0u xanh s\\u1eefa, v\\u1ecb r\\u1ea5t ng\\u1ecdt, kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u00e1t, kh\\u00f4ng h\\u1ea1t v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u01a1m \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng<\\/p><p>H\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb b\\u00e9o ng\\u1eady \\u0111\\u1ecdng l\\u1ea1i \\u1edf cu\\u1ed1ng h\\u1ecdng sau khi \\u0103n<\\/p><p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"content\":\"<h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255,102,0);\\\"><span><strong>1. Gi\\u1ed1ng v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7ng lo\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c<\\/strong><\\/span> &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n H\\u00e0n hay nho Shine Muscat, nho xanh s\\u1eefa, nho s\\u1eefa l\\u00e0 gi\\u1ed1ng nho lai t\\u1ea1o. Th\\u1ee9c qu\\u1ea3 n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u1ed1i gi\\u1ed1ng gi\\u1eefa lo\\u1ea1i nho Akitsu-21 v\\u00e0 Hakunan n\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0o lo\\u1ea1i nho l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng b\\u1ed9i. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u d\\u00e0y d\\u1ea1n t\\u1eeb Vi\\u1ec7n Khoa h\\u1ecdc C\\u00e2y \\u0103n qu\\u1ea3 Qu\\u1ed1c gia (NIFTS) t\\u1ea1i Nh\\u1eadt B\\u1ea3n c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 n\\u0103m 1988.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Do k\\u1ebf th\\u1eeba t\\u1eeb hai gi\\u1ed1ng nho Akitsu-21 v\\u00e0 Hakunan, nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 \\u01b0u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng. Ch\\u1eb3ng h\\u1ea1n, lo\\u1ea1i nho Hakunan thu\\u1ed9c gi\\u1ed1ng c\\u00f3 h\\u1ea1t l\\u1edbn t\\u1ea1i ch\\u00e2u \\u00c2u, lai gi\\u1eefa Kaiji v\\u00e0 Cattacurgan. N\\u00ean cho qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00f3 h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ed1t. V\\u1edbi gi\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ee9 hai l\\u00e0 Akitsu-21, lai gi\\u1eefa Steuben v\\u00e0 Muscat, c\\u00f3 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng cao k\\u00e8m k\\u1ebft c\\u1ea5u v\\u00e0 h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-70640 aligncenter entered litespeed-loaded\\\" style=\\\"border-style:none;height:auto;margin:0px auto 20px;max-width:100%;text-align:center;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/06\\/DSCF7018-800x800.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"800\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/06\\/DSCF7018-800x800.jpg\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">V\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng t\\u0103ng, H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00f3 13.388 ha v\\u01b0\\u1eddn nho so v\\u1edbi 12.795 ha c\\u1ee7a n\\u0103m 2018. Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, 3.579 ha, t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng 26,7%, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u1ed3ng nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n H\\u00e0n. V\\u00e0o n\\u0103m 2018, ch\\u1ec9 c\\u00f3 7,4% t\\u1ed5ng s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng cho nho Shine Muscat. Trong khi ch\\u1ec9 14,5% \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0o n\\u0103m 2019. M\\u1ed9t \\u0111i\\u1ec1u kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 kh\\u00f4ng nh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1ebfn, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti\\u00eau d\\u00f9ng ng\\u00e0y nay th\\u00edch tr\\u00e1i c\\u00e2y m\\u00e0 h\\u1ecd c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0103n m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n g\\u1ecdt v\\u1ecf. \\u0110\\u00e2y c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 g\\u00f3p ph\\u1ea7n th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y s\\u1ef1 ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn c\\u1ee7a nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Nho Shine Muscat c\\u00f3 ch\\u00f9m m\\u1ecdc sum su\\u00ea, t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o th\\u00e0nh h\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ee5, tr\\u1ecdng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng kho\\u1ea3ng t\\u1eeb 400-500g\\/ch\\u00f9m. \\u0110\\u1ebfn m\\u00f9a ch\\u00edn, nho mang m\\u00e0u xanh l\\u1ee5c v\\u00e0ng, v\\u1ecf b\\u00ean ngo\\u00e0i m\\u1ecbn b\\u00f3ng, kh\\u00f4ng nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 m\\u1ecdng n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. Khi th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c, nho c\\u00f3 v\\u1ecb ng\\u1ecdt \\u0111\\u1eadm \\u0111\\u00e0, gi\\u00f2n ngon, l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng cao v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng s\\u1eefa \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255,102,0);\\\"><span><strong>2. M\\u00f9a v\\u1ee5 &amp; thu ho\\u1ea1ch nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u1edf H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c<\\/strong><\\/span> &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">T\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i, ch\\u01b0a gi\\u1ed1ng nho n\\u00e0o c\\u00f3 m\\u1ee9c gi\\u00e1 v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t m\\u1eb7t nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n. S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu m\\u1ee9c gi\\u00e1 thu\\u1ed9c premium class l\\u00e0 do qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c h\\u1ebft s\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t. Nho \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ed3ng ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n h\\u1eefu c\\u01a1, trong nh\\u00e0 k\\u00ednh v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ti\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfn nh\\u1ea5t. M\\u1ed9t th\\u00f4ng tin th\\u00fa v\\u1ecb v\\u1ec1 gi\\u1ed1ng nho \\u0111\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ecf n\\u00e0y, ch\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ta s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng c\\u1eaft b\\u1ecf 30-40% s\\u1ed1 ch\\u00f9m nho tr\\u00ean c\\u00e2y, \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o 1 nh\\u00e1nh ch\\u1ec9 c\\u00f3 1 ch\\u00f9m, do \\u0111\\u00f3 t\\u1eebng qu\\u1ea3 nho s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng, cho ra lo\\u1ea1i nho c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Nho m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u01a1n H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9a v\\u1ee5 t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 6 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 11 d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng l\\u1ecbch.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-70641 aligncenter entered litespeed-loaded\\\" style=\\\"border-style:none;height:auto;margin:0px auto 20px;max-width:100%;text-align:center;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/06\\/nho-mau-don-3-800x800.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"800\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/06\\/nho-mau-don-3-800x800.jpg\\\"><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background