b(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>Cherry \\u0111\\u1ecf&nbsp;M\\u1ef9 <\\/strong><i>(hay tr\\u00e1i anh \\u0111\\u00e0o M\\u1ef9)<\\/i>&nbsp;\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ed3ng&nbsp;chuy\\u00ean canh t\\u1ea1i&nbsp;mi\\u1ec1n T\\u00e2y B\\u1eafc M\\u1ef9 \\u1edf 5 bang g\\u1ed3m: Washington, Oregon, Idaho, Montana v\\u00e0 Utah v\\u1edbi&nbsp;s\\u1ea3n l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cherry \\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u00ednh kho\\u1ea3ng t\\u1eeb 25 tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ebfn 30 tri\\u1ec7u th\\u00f9ng (th\\u00f9ng 5kg) m\\u1ed7i n\\u0103m. Hai gi\\u1ed1ng cherry M\\u1ef9 ch\\u00ednh bao g\\u1ed3m: gi\\u1ed1ng<strong> SWEET&nbsp;cherries<\\/strong> (Prunus avium) v\\u00e0 gi\\u1ed1ng <strong>TART&nbsp;or \\u201csour\\u201d cherries<\\/strong> (Prunus cerasus), trong \\u0111\\u00f3 gi\\u1ed1ng Sweet ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu ph\\u1ee5c v\\u1ee5 th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u00e1i c\\u00e2y t\\u01b0\\u01a1i, c\\u00f2n gi\\u1ed1ng TART ph\\u1ee5c v\\u1ee5 ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn cherry s\\u1ea5y, cherry kh\\u00f4 v.v<\\/p><div class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:11.7px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px 0px 15px;max-width:100%;padding:0px;text-align:center;width:2343px;word-spacing:0px;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_15325\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-62456 size-medium entered litespeed-loaded\\\" style=\\\"border-style:none;height:auto;margin:0px auto 20px;max-width:100%;text-align:center;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/02\\/cherry-do-my-vinfruits-2-800x800.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"800\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" data-src=\\\"https:\\/\\/vinfruits.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/02\\/cherry-do-my-vinfruits-2-800x800.jpg\\\"><\\/p><p class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.53px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-15325\\\">Cherry M\\u1ef9 ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ed3ng t\\u1ea1i Washington, California, Oregon, Idaho, Montana v\\u00e0 Utah<\\/p><\\/div><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">\\u0110\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng c\\u1ee7a tr\\u00e1i cherry \\u0111\\u1ecf M\\u1ef9&nbsp;l\\u00e0<strong> tr\\u00e1i to, ch\\u1eafc, c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0ng k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf t\\u01b0\\u01a1i<\\/strong>, khi ch\\u00edn c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf g\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u1eadm, b\\u00ean trong&nbsp;th\\u1ecbt nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u00f3 m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ecf nh\\u1ea1t, h\\u1ea1t nh\\u1ecf khi \\u0103n kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ecb d\\u00ednh th\\u1ecbt v\\u00e0o h\\u1ea1t t\\u1ea1o c\\u1ea3m gi\\u00e1c r\\u1ea5t s\\u1ea3ng kho\\u00e1i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Cherry M\\u1ef9 l\\u00e0 lo\\u1ea1i cherry \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c y\\u00eau th\\u00edch nh\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea1i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam do th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u00e0ng kh\\u00f4ng, tr\\u00e1i t\\u01b0\\u01a1i, c\\u1ee9ng v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 v\\u1ecb ng\\u1ecdt \\u0111\\u1eadm \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255,102,0);\\\"><span><strong>2. M\\u00f9a v\\u1ee5 &amp; thu ho\\u1ea1ch&nbsp;Cherry t\\u01b0\\u01a1i \\u1edf M\\u1ef9<\\/strong><\\/span>&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Tr\\u00e1i cherry M\\u1ef9 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c <i>thu ho\\u1ea1ch t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 5 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 9 h\\u00e0ng n\\u0103m<\\/i>, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thu ho\\u1ea1ch b\\u1eb1ng tay, ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1eb1ng m\\u00e1y; v\\u1eadn chuy\\u1ec3n t\\u1edbi nh\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3i, do \\u0111\\u00f3 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng tr\\u00e1i cherry&nbsp;r\\u1ea5t&nbsp;cao.<\\/p><div class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:11.7px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px 0px 15px;max-width:100%;padding:0px;text-align:center;width:2343px;word-spacing:0px;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_15326\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><p class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.53px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-15326\\\">Cherry M\\u1ef9 c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9a t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 5 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 9 h\\u00e0ng n\\u0103m<\\/p><\\/div><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Chi ph\\u00ed cho vi\\u1ec7c h\\u00e1i th\\u1ee7 c\\u00f4ng n\\u00e0y kh\\u00e1 cao, nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u00e1i cherry kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ecb x\\u01b0\\u1edbc, r\\u1ee5ng cu\\u1ed1ng, h\\u1ecfng qu\\u1ea3.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Sau&nbsp;khi ki\\u1ec3m tra ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u00f4ng quan, tr\\u00e1i cherry t\\u01b0\\u01a1i M\\u1ef9 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3i th\\u00e0nh c\\u00e1c th\\u00f9ng 5.0 \\u2013 10kg, x\\u1ebfp trong c\\u00e1c Pallet (m\\u1ed7i pallet t\\u1eeb 150 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 200 th\\u00f9ng) v\\u00e0 b\\u1ecdc ngo\\u00e0i b\\u1eb1ng t\\u1ea5m c\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ed9 l\\u1ea1nh cho cherry.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255,102,0);\\\"><span>2. Gi\\u00e1 Cherry \\u0111\\u1ecf M\\u1ef9 nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u bao nhi\\u00eau?<\\/span>&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><i>Cherry M\\u1ef9 bao nhi\\u00eau ti\\u1ec1n 1kg<\\/i> lu\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 c\\u00e2u h\\u1ecfi b\\u0103n kho\\u0103n c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c t\\u00edn \\u0111\\u1ed3 tr\\u00e1i cherry v\\u1edbi th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u00e1i cherry nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u h\\u1ed7n lo\\u1ea1n nh\\u01b0 ng\\u00e0y nay. S\\u1ebd kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3&nbsp;cho b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1i cherry m\\u1ef9 n\\u00e0o, ngay t\\u1ea1i v\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ea5t b\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ecba, gi\\u00e1 cherry c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 s\\u1ef1 ch\\u00eanh l\\u1ec7ch gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c bang ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng ty ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i, m\\u1ed7i c\\u00f4ng ty l\\u1ea1i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t m\\u1ee9c gi\\u00e1 kh\\u00e1c nhau.<\\/p><div class=\\\"wp-caption aligncenter\\\" style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:11.7px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0px 0px 15px;max-width:100%;padding: