34px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255,102,0);\\\"><span><strong>CHERRY \\u0110\\u1ece SIZE 9.5 M\\u1ef8 \\u2013 CH\\u00cdNH HI\\u1ec6U<\\/strong><\\/span> &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/h2><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><i>100% n\\u00f3i kh\\u00f4ng v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ea5t b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n &amp; tr\\u00e1i c\\u00e2y Trung Qu\\u1ed1c!<\\/i><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;text-align:left;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255,102,0);\\\"><span><strong>1. Gi\\u1ed1ng v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ee7ng lo\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a tr\\u00e1i Cherry \\u0111\\u1ecf&nbsp;M\\u1ef9<\\/strong><\\/span> &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>Cherry \\u0111\\u1ecf&nbsp;M\\u1ef9 <\\/strong><i>(hay tr\\u00e1i anh \\u0111\\u00e0o M\\u1ef9)<\\/i>&nbsp;\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ed3ng&nbsp;chuy\\u00ean canh t\\u1ea1i&nbsp;mi\\u1ec1n T\\u00e2y B\\u1eafc M\\u1ef9 \\u1edf 5 bang g\\u1ed3m: Washington, Oregon, Idaho, Montana v\\u00e0 Utah v\\u1edbi&nbsp;s\\u1ea3n l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cherry \\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u00ednh kho\\u1ea3ng t\\u1eeb 25 tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ebfn 30 tri\\u1ec7u th\\u00f9ng (th\\u00f9ng 5kg) m\\u1ed7i n\\u0103m. Hai gi\\u1ed1ng cherry M\\u1ef9 ch\\u00ednh bao g\\u1ed3m: gi\\u1ed1ng<strong> SWEET&nbsp;cherries<\\/strong> (Prunus avium) v\\u00e0 gi\\u1ed1ng <strong>TART&nbsp;or \\u201csour\\u201d cherries<\\/strong> (Prunus cerasus), trong \\u0111\\u00f3 gi\\u1ed1ng Sweet ch\\