gn:center;width:2343px;word-spacing:0px;\\\" id=\\\"attachment_15326\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><p class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.53px;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;text-align:center;\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-15326\\\">Cherry M\\u1ef9 c\\u00f3 m\\u00f9a t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 5 \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u00e1ng 9 h\\u00e0ng n\\u0103m<\\/p><\\/div><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Chi ph\\u00ed cho vi\\u1ec7c h\\u00e1i th\\u1ee7 c\\u00f4ng n\\u00e0y kh\\u00e1 cao, nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u00e1i cherry kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ecb x\\u01b0\\u1edbc, r\\u1ee5ng cu\\u1ed1ng, h\\u1ecfng qu\\u1ea3.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Sau&nbsp;khi ki\\u1ec3m tra ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u00f4ng quan, tr\\u00e1i cherry t\\u01b0\\u01a1i M\\u1ef9 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3i th\\u00e0nh c\\u00e1c th\\u00f9ng 5.0 \\u2013 10kg, x\\u1ebfp trong c\\u00e1c Pallet (m\\u1ed7i pallet t\\u1eeb 150 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 200 th\\u00f9ng) v\\u00e0 b\\u1ecdc ngo\\u00e0i b\\u1eb1ng t\\u1ea5m c\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ed9 l\\u1ea1nh cho cherry.<\\/p><h3 style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;margin:40px 0px 20px;padding:0px;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:rgb(255,102,0);\\\"><span>2. Gi\\u00e1 Cherry \\u0111\\u1ecf M\\u1ef9 nh\\u1eadp kh\\u1ea9u bao nhi\\u00eau?<\\/span> &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(69,69,69);font-family:Manrope, sans-serif;font-si